White Mountain Capital Management Form D
The New Jersey-based White Mountain Capital Management, Lp filed Form D regarding $22.00 million offering. The date of first sale was 2013-11-29. The Limited Partnership raised $22.00 million. The offering is still open. The total offering amount amount was $22.00 million. The form was filed on 2015-11-20. White Mountain Capital Management, Lp’s clarification was: Devorah Capital, LLC and its affiliates receive customary management fees and/or performance allocations as described in the Issuer’s Confidential Private Placement Memorandum.. 
 White Mountain Capital Management is based in New Jersey. The firm’s business is Pooled Investment Fund. The D form was filed by Joseph R Weiss Managing Member of the Issuer’s General Partner. The company was incorporated in 2013. The filler’s address is: C/O Devorah Capital, Llc, 1536 East 28Th Street, Brooklyn, Ny, New York, 11229. Devorah Capital, Llc is the related person in the form and it has address: 1536 East 28Th Street, Brooklyn, Ny, New York, 11229. Link to White Mountain Capital Management Filing: 000159250315000001.
Analysis of White Mountain Capital Management Offering
On average, startups in the Pooled Investment Fund sector, sell 37.80 % pooled investment fund interests. White Mountain Capital Management sold 100.00 % of the offering. The average investment offering size is $24.76 million for companies in the Pooled Investment Fund industry sector. The total amount raised is 11.13 % smaller than the average for companies in the Pooled Investment Fund sector. 

